WALL OF THE EYELESS - Wimfolsfestta Bundle. CD+T-Shirt for a discounted price.

This CD issue is the high quality factory press on silver CD in digipak packaging with expanded artwork and the 12-page booklet. Limited to 300 copies. 
The ultimate listening and visual experience.

The shirt is the first ever and very limited Wall Of The Eyeless T-Shirt. Printed in Sweden. 
High quality screen print on Fruit Of The Loom T-Shirts.

After receiving a lot of good and great feedback after the release of the first demo, “Through Emptiness”, the band got an opportunity to push everything to a new level. This record, which is entitled “Wimfolsfestta”, is basically Wall Of The Eyeless's second demo, but it's much more than that.
It has 4 tracks with the total running time of almost 27 minutes, which were recorded and mixed in Endarker Studio (MARDUK, FUNERAL MIST, RAGNAROK, etc.) with MARDUK’s bassist Magnus “Devo” Andersson as a producer and mastered by Jens Bogren at Fascination Street Studios (KATATONIA, SWALLOW THE SUN, OPETH, AMON AMARTH, BLOODBATH, etc.).
“Wimfolsfestta” is a big step up both production- and songwriting-wise. 

