"It is astonishing to me that Wall of the Eyeless are without a record deal. Their debut demo Through Emptiness received an amazing response and their follow up Wimfolsfestta is remarkable in its growth. Combining progressive elements with brutal death metal showcases a band that is ready to make the jump to the next level. The musicianship and songwriting are top notch." 
- Unsigned band of the month at heavymetal.about.com - May 2013 

"Everything about the release is top notch down to the packaging and presentation and I truly hope these guys continue to release music of this quality and that a label notices them and gives them much more exposure as they are one of the more promising unsigned acts I have heard recently." 
